properties.name: aquasecurity:trivy:Labels:description
properties.value: This image contains the Open Liberty runtime with IBM Semeru Runtime Open Edition OpenJDK 17 with OpenJ9 and Red Hat UBI 9 minimal as the base OS.  For more information on this image please see https://github.com/OpenLiberty/ci.docker#building-an-application-image

properties.name: aquasecurity:trivy:Labels:io.k8s.description
properties.value: The Universal Base Image Minimal is a stripped down image that uses microdnf as a package manager. This base image is freely redistributable, but Red Hat only supports Red Hat technologies through subscriptions for Red Hat products. This image is maintained by Red Hat and updated regularly.
